  "book.skystone.creators_gratitude.title": "SkyStone Creator's Book",
  "book.skystone.creators_gratitude.page1": "Seriously, you did it? Every single advancement?\n\nIt's one thing to write the code for this mod, but actually watching someone gather the full meteorite set, survive a crazy 100-block fall, and summon a whole army of golems to crush the Wither... That is wild!",
  "book.skystone.creators_gratitude.page2": "Thank you for spending your time with SkyStone and completing it. As the creator, this is the best reward I could ask for.\n\nGood luck in your next worlds!\n\n— AmedoNai.",
  "book.skystone.creators_gratitude.page3": "If you'd like to leave a review, comment, or even suggest an idea, feel free to message me on my Discord or Telegram account. I'll be sure to respond!\nDiscord: amedonai,\nTelegram: amedo_nai"
